SUMMARY:Romance Book Club: The Bride Test
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nOkay romance book lovers\, the next 
 book we will be reading is: The Bride Test by Helen Hoang.\n\nWe’ll be m
 eeting again at Namu and I’ll try to show up a bit early to save us a sp
 ot.\n\nCan’t wait it to see y’all there!
